   MotoGP 13 doesn't allow for game modifications as is, nor it does allow to
   mantain third-party modified game files during online gaming, forcing   to
   quit the game, reinstall or copy over the original data files and  restart
   the game.
   
   This patch allows to play with mods to data files, such as community  made
   bugfixes, game balancing mods and whatsoever.
   
   This is not intended to be used as a way to cheat.
